id: pm-401l
title: Extract shared direct CLI spawn helper for integration tests
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: tests duplicate direct dist CLI resolution/spawn helpers. Representative copies are tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts:8 distCliPath, tests/integration/governance-presets.integration.spec.ts:15 distCliPath and :19 runDistCli, plus existing helper-like logic in tests/helpers/withTempPmPath.ts:21 distCliPath and :189 runNodeCli. This repeats process.execPath + dist/cli.js resolution + stdout/stderr/status capture and sometimes JSON parsing."
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 3
tags[4]: cli,code-quality,dedup,tests
