author: codex-duplicate-audit
acceptance_criteria: A shared direct CLI runner/distCliPath helper exists for tests that need raw process execution; integration specs use it instead of local copies; stdout/stderr/status and JSON parsing behavior remain explicit; targeted integration tests and pnpm build pass.
