  "2026-05-23T19:14:37.707Z",codex-cli-error-helper-agent,"Start: inspecting duplicated dist CLI spawn helpers in tests/helpers/withTempPmPath.ts, tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts, tests/integration/governance-presets.integration.spec.ts, and raw dist runs in release/help runtime specs; plan is to add/reuse a shared direct dist runner with stdout/stderr/status plus env/cwd/stdin support, then migrate clear call sites only."
  "2026-05-23T19:22:03.629Z",codex-cli-error-helper-agent,"Evidence: pnpm build passed. Focused verification passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/governance-presets.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts => 4 files passed, 139 tests passed, duration 188.26s. Implemented shared direct dist CLI runner and migrated local direct-runner clones plus clear raw dist stdin/non-owner calls; left shell pipeline spawn local because it specifically verifies bash pipefail/EPIPE behavior."
